<p style='font-size:13.5pt'><span style='font-weight:bold;
font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=en-US>Sring </span><span style='font-weight:
bold;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"' lang=zh-CN>框架结构</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>是分层的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Java SE/EE </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>一站式轻量级开源框架</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=136 height=136 alt="Spring Framework (@springframework) / Twitter"></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>以</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> IoC</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Inverse of Control</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，控制反转）和</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> AOP</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Aspect Oriented
     Programming</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>，面向切面编程）为内核。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=480 height=370 alt=spring-overview></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>IoC </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>指的是将对象的创建权交给</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Spring </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>去创建。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>使用</span><span style='font-family:
"Comic Sans MS"'> Spring </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>之前，对象的创建都是由我们使用</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> new </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>创建，而使用</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> Spring </span><span style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>之后，对象的创建都交给了</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>
Spring </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>框架。</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>AOP </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>用来封装多个类的公共行为，将那些与业务无关，却为业务模块所共同调用的逻辑封装起来，减少系统的重复代码，降低模块间的耦合度。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>另外，</span><span style='font-family:
"Comic Sans MS"'>AOP </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>还解决一些系统层面上的问题，比如日志、事务、权限等。</span></p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-size:13.5pt'><span style='font-weight:bold;
font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=en-US>Spring</span><span style='font-weight:
bold;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"' lang=zh-CN>的特点</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Spring </span><span style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>框架具有以下几个特点。</span></p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=1 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;
     color:#ED7D31'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:
     12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>方便解耦，简化开发</span></li>
 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>就是一个大工厂，可以将所有对象的创建和依赖关系的维护交给</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Spring </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>管理。</span></li>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>IoC</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>容器降低了业务对象替换的复杂性，提高了组件之间的解耦</span></li>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>ORM</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>和</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>DAO</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>提供了与第三方持久层框架的良好整合，并简化了底层的数据库访问</span></li>
 </ul>
</ol>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=2 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;
     color:#ED7D31'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:
     12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>方便集成各种优秀框架</span></li>
 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>不排斥各种优秀的开源框架，其内部提供了对各种优秀框架（如</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Struts2</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>、</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Hibernate</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>、</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MyBatis </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>等）的直接支持。</span></li>
 </ul>
</ol>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
 0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
 font-style:normal'>
 <li value=3 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;
     color:#ED7D31'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:
     12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>降低</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'> Java EE API </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>的使用难度</span></li>
 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的高度开放性，并不强制应用完全依赖于</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，开发者可自由选用</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>框架的部分或全部。</span></li>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>对</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Java EE </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>开发中非常难用的一些</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> API</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>（</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>JDBC</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>、</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>JavaMail</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>、远程调用等）都提供了封装，使这些</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> API </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>应用的难度大大降低。</span></li>
 </ul>
</ol>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:

 <li value=4 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;

 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;

  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span

  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span

      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Spring</span><span

      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Write Once</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Run Anywhere</span><span
